#. (itstool) path: component/name
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:10
msgid "Zanshin"
msgstr "Zanshin"

#. (itstool) path: component/summary
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:11
msgid "To Do Management Application"
msgstr "待办事项管理应用"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:13
msgid ""
"Zanshin is a powerful yet simple application for managing your day to day "
"actions. It helps you organize and reduce the cognitive pressure of what one "
"has to do in his job and personal life. You'll never forget anything "
"anymore, getting your mind like water."
msgstr ""
"Zanshin 是一个强大而简明的应用程序，可用来管理您的日常操作。 它帮助您组织并减"
"少人们在工作和个人生活中必须做的事情造成的认知压力。 您再也不会不会忘记任何东"
"西，让您心如止水。"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:18
msgid "Collect"
msgstr "收集"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:19
msgid ""
"Worried about forgetting something? Unexpected memory losses? Zanshin is "
"here to help you. You can collect your tasks and free your mind. You will "
"soon stop hearing this voice nagging you about what you probably forgot, or "
"what you should do. Just fire up Zanshin, once something is collected, you "
"are sure to find it there."
msgstr ""
"担心忘记东西吗？有意外失忆吗？让Zanshin来帮助您。您可以集中管理您的任务并放飞"
"您的心灵。 您很快就能摆脱那些提醒“您忘了什么东西”或“您该做什么了”的唠叨。只需"
"让Zanshin为您效劳：任何东西被收集，您都能在这找到它。"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:20
msgid "Organize"
msgstr "整理"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:21
msgid ""
"Zanshin makes it simple to put your daily life in order. Just create a few "
"projects, a few contexts and start filling them with tasks. You can simply "
"do this using drag and drop. Something has to be done before a given day? "
"Just set a due date and it'll stand out from your other items. You need to "
"work on a project? Focus on it and you will see all the related tasks. "
"Feeling like dealing with your phone calls? Focus on your phone context to "
"find all the pending calls you have to give."
msgstr ""
"Zanshin让搞定您的生活变得简单。只需创建几个项目，几个情景并开始用任务填满它"
"们。 您仅需拖放就能做到这一点。 必须在某天前完成？只需设置一个到期日，任务就"
"会与其他项目区分开。 需要在一个项目上工作？关注它，您就能看到所有相关任务。 "
"要处理您的电话？关注您的电话上下文就能找到您要拨打的所有待处理电话。"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:22
msgid "Optimize"
msgstr "优化"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:23
msgid ""
"We hackers love our keyboards, and you probably find yourself more efficient "
"with your hands on the keyboard as much as possible. That's why we crafted "
"Zanshin carefully to be completely drivable from the keyboard. We added "
"shortcuts to add tasks, move them to a project or a context, navigate, etc."
msgstr ""
"我们极客热爱键盘。您很可能发现，您的手与键盘搭档时您会更高效。正因为如此，我"
"们精心雕琢了Zanshin，使其完全顺从于您的键盘。 我们加入了导航、添加任务、将项"
"移动到项目或情景等的捷径。"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:24
msgid "Integrate"
msgstr "融合"

#. (itstool) path: description/p
#: org.kde.zanshin.metainfo.xml:25
msgid ""
"Zanshin is an application of the KDE community, as such it unleashes even "
"more power when used with other KDE Applications or within KDE Plasma "
"Desktop. Using KMail? You can create a task right from an email you received "
"and it'll appear in Zanshin's Inbox. Using KOrganizer? All your overdue and "
"coming task will appear in the calendar view. Using Plasma Desktop? Then you "
"can collect from anywhere using KRunner, just type in \"todo: Buy apples\", "
"and you will find that tasks in Zanshin's Inbox, even if it wasn't running!"
msgstr ""
"Zanshin 是 KDE 社区的应用程序， 因此当配合其他 KDE 应用程序使用或在 KDE "
"Plasma 桌面内使用时，它甚至能发挥更多的能力。使用 KMail吗？从您收到的电子邮件"
"就能直接创建任务，并且它会出现在Zanshin收件箱中。 使用 KOrganizer吗？您逾期的"
"和将来的任务都会出现在日历视图中。 使用 Plasma 桌面吗？ 那您可以使用 KRunner "
"随时随地收集，只需输入“待办：购买苹果”， 你就能在Zanshin收件箱找到任务，即使"
"Zanshin没有运行！"

